" Reverse word's case
inoremap <A-u> <esc>mzg~iw`za
"Better VIM version
"inoremap <C-u> <esc>mz^f;bv`z:s/\%V;/_/g<cr>`z:noh<cr>a<esc>mzg~iw`za
